@node Bugs
                                       @{b}@{u}BUGS!!!!!!!!!@{ub}@{uu}


   Don't worry there aren't that many.

   But if you find one,or if you're in trouble,please write!

   Some strange things still remain but who cares?

    - If you want a fine guru,try to DISPLAY a very big and colourful picture.

    - The final picture mustn't be too big(I mean:not 36000*2600*256...)

    - Only IFF for the moment (use HappyDT or the shareware MPLSPatch)

@endnode Bugs

@node Histoire
                              @{b}@{u}History and a bright future@{ub}@{uu}


  *@{b}History...@{ub}

   - ??? : version 1.0 : only released on "Dream44" CD-Rom.Apparenty nobody noticed it.

   - september 1997 - version 1.05 : Unreleased (?);bug fixes,font-sensitive interface,
     a lot faster.

   - Summer 1999 - version 1.05b : first official public release;a few bug fixes.

    To me,WM1.05b works fine,so it may be the last version.


  *@{b}Future@{ub}:

   -  maybe Datatype handling.Who needs it?
   -  will I find some time and motivation to make it faster?(ask for it..)
   -  will I find some time and motivation to change the pics display?(maybe if  you
      ask...)
   -  do you really need a better-looking interface with several pictures loaded  at
      the same time,drag'n'drop,rainbow colours and so on???
   -  in fact,if you want anything you can ask and I'll see what I can do.
@endnode Histoire


